msgid "Pausing games and process mode"
msgstr "Cluichí agus modh próisis a chur ar sos"

msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Réamhrá"

msgid ""
"In most games it is desirable to, at some point, interrupt the game to do "
"something else, such as taking a break or changing options. Implementing a "
"fine-grained control for what can be paused (and what cannot) is a lot of "
"work, so a simple framework for pausing is provided in Godot."
msgstr ""
"I bhformhór na gcluichí tá sé inmhianaithe, ag pointe éigin, cur isteach ar "
"an gcluiche chun rud éigin eile a dhéanamh, mar shampla sos a thógáil nó "
"roghanna a athrú. Is mór oibre é rialú mionghráinneach a chur i bhfeidhm "
"maidir leis an méid is féidir a stopadh (agus cad nach féidir), mar sin "
"cuirtear creat simplí chun sos a chur ar fáil i Godot."

msgid "How pausing works"
msgstr "Conas a oibríonn sos"

msgid ""
"To pause the game the pause state must be set. This is done by assigning "
"``true`` to the :ref:`SceneTree.paused <class_SceneTree_property_paused>` "
"property:"
msgstr ""
"Chun an cluiche a chur ar sos ní mór an staid sos a shocrú. Déantar é seo "
"trí ``true`` a shannadh don mhaoin :ref:`SceneTree.paused "
"<class_SceneTree_property_paused>`:"

msgid ""
"Doing this will cause two things. First, 2D and 3D physics will be stopped "
"for all nodes. Second, the behavior of certain nodes will stop or start "
"depending on their process mode."
msgstr ""
"Déanfaidh sé seo beidh dhá rud mar thoradh ar dhá rud. Ar dtús, stopfar "
"fisic 2D agus 3D do gach nóid. Ar an dara dul síos, stopfaidh nó tosóidh "
"iompar nóid áirithe ag brath ar a mhodh próisis."

msgid ""
"The physics servers can be made active while the game is paused by using "
"their ``set_active`` methods."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir na freastalaithe fisice a dhéanamh gníomhach agus an cluiche a "
"stopadh trína gcuid modhanna `set_active` a úsáid."

msgid "Process Modes"
msgstr "Modhanna Próisis"

msgid ""
"Each node in Godot has a \"Process Mode\" that defines when it processes. It "
"can be found and changed under a node's :ref:`Node <class_Node>` properties "
"in the inspector."
msgstr ""
"Tá \"Mód Próisis\" ag gach nód i Godot a shainíonn nuair a phróiseálann sé. "
"Is féidir é a aimsiú agus a athrú faoi réadmhaoin nód :ref:`Node "
"<class_Node>` sa chigire."

msgid "You can also alter the property with code:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat an maoin a athrú le cód freisin:"

msgid "This is what each mode tells a node to do:"
msgstr "Seo a insíonn gach modh do nód le déanamh:"

msgid ""
"**Inherit**: Process depending on the state of the parent, grandparent, etc. "
"The first parent that has a non-Inherit state."
msgstr ""
"**Oidhreacht**: Próiseas ag brath ar staid an tuismitheora, "
"seantuismitheora, srl. An chéad thuismitheoir a bhfuil stát neamh-"
"oidhreachta aige."

msgid ""
"**Pausable**: Process the node (and its children in Inherit mode) only when "
"the game is not paused."
msgstr ""
"**Stopáil**: Próiseáil an nód (agus a pháistí i mód Oidhreacht) ach amháin "
"nuair nach ndéantar an cluiche a stopadh."

msgid ""
"**WhenPaused**: Process the node (and its children in Inherit mode) *only* "
"when the game is paused."
msgstr ""
"**When Seased**: Próiseáil an nód (agus a pháistí i mód Oidhreacht) *amháin* "
"nuair a chuirtear an cluiche stop."

msgid ""
"**Always**: Process the node (and its children in Inherit mode) no matter "
"what. Paused or not, this node will process."
msgstr ""
"**I gcónaí**: Próiseáil an nód (agus a leanaí i mód Oidhreachta) is cuma cad "
"é. Sos nó nach bhfuil, próiseálfaidh an nód seo."

msgid ""
"**Disabled**: The node (and its children in Inherit mode) will not process "
"at all."
msgstr ""
"**Díchumas**: Ní phróiseálfaidh an nód (agus a leanaí i mód Oidhreacht) ar "
"chor ar bith."

msgid ""
"By default, all nodes have this property in the \"Inherit\" state. If the "
"parent is set to \"Inherit\", then the grandparent will be checked and so "
"on. If a state can't be found in any of the grandparents, the pause state in "
"SceneTree is used. This means that, by default, when the game is paused "
"every node will be paused. Several things happen when a node stops "
"processing."
msgstr ""
"De réir réamhshocraithe, tá an maoin seo ag gach nóid sa stát “Oidhreacht”. "
"Má tá an tuismitheoir socraithe go “Oidhreacht”, ansin déanfar an "
"seantuismitheoir a sheiceáil agus mar sin de. Mura féidir stát a fháil in "
"aon cheann de na seantuismitheoirí, úsáidtear an stát sos i SceneTree. "
"Ciallaíonn sé seo go gcuirfear stop ar gach nód, de réir réamhshocraithe, "
"nuair a chuirtear an cluiche ar sos. Tarlaíonn roinnt rudaí nuair a stopann "
"nód ag próiseáil."

msgid ""
"The ``_process``, ``_physics_process``, ``_input``, and ``_input_event`` "
"functions will not be called. However signals still work and cause their "
"connected function to run, even if that function's script is attached to a "
"node that is not currently being processed."
msgstr ""
"Ní ghlaofar ar na feidhmeanna ``_process``, `_physics_process``, `_input``, "
"agus ``_input_event``. Mar sin féin, oibríonn comharthaí fós agus cuireann "
"siad ar a bhfeidhm nasctha a rith, fiú má tá script na feidhme sin "
"ceangailte le nód nach bhfuil á phróiseáil faoi láthair."

msgid ""
"Animation nodes will pause their current animation, audio nodes will pause "
"their current audio stream, and particles will pause. These resume "
"automatically when the game is no longer paused."
msgstr ""
"Cuirfidh nóid bheochan a mbeochan reatha ar sos, sosóidh nóid fuaime a sruth "
"fuaime reatha, agus sosóidh na cáithníní. Atosóidh siad seo go huathoibríoch "
"nuair nach bhfuil an cluiche ar sos a thuilleadh."

msgid ""
"It is important to note that even if a node is processing while the game is "
"paused physics will **NOT** work for it by default. As stated earlier this "
"is because the physics servers are turned off. The physics servers can be "
"made active while the game is paused by using their ``set_active`` methods."
msgstr ""
"Tá sé tábhachtach a thabhairt faoi deara go n-oibreoidh fiú má tá nód ag "
"próiseáil agus an cluiche ag sos go n-oibreoidh an fisice** NÍO** dó de réir "
"réamhshocraithe. Mar a dúradh níos luaithe tá sé seo toisc go bhfuil na "
"freastalaithe fisice a mhúchadh. Is féidir na freastalaithe fisice a "
"dhéanamh gníomhach agus an cluiche a stopadh trína gcuid modhanna "
"`set_active` a úsáid."

msgid "Pause menu example"
msgstr "Sampla roghchlár sos"

msgid "Start by creating a button that will be used to pause the game."
msgstr ""
"Tosaigh trí chnaipe a chruthú a úsáidfear chun an cluiche a chur ar sos."

msgid ""
"Create a menu containing a close button, set the **Process Mode** of the "
"menu's root node to **When Paused**, then hide the menu. Since the process "
"mode is set to **When Paused** on the root node, all its children and "
"grandchildren will inherit that process mode. This way, all the nodes in the "
"menu will start processing when the game is paused."
msgstr ""
"Cruthaigh roghchlár ina bhfuil cnaipe dlúnadh, socraigh an **Mód Próiseas** "
"de nód fréimhe an roghchláir chuig **Nuair a Seasaítear **, ansin folaigh an "
"roghchlár. Ós rud é go bhfuil an modh próisis socraithe u**Nuair a "
"Seasaítear ** ar an nód fréimhe, beidh a pháistí agus a ghlanna páistí go "
"léir an modh próisis sin oidhreachta. Ar an mbealach seo, tosóidh na nóid go "
"léir sa roghchlár ag próiseáil nuair a chuirtear an cluiche stop."

msgid ""
"Attach a script to the menu's root node, connect the pause button created "
"earlier to a new method in the script, and inside that method pause the game "
"and show the pause menu."
msgstr ""
"Ceangail script le nód fréimhe an roghchláir, ceangail an cnaipe sos a "
"cruthaíodh níos luaithe le modh nua sa script, agus taobh istigh den mhodh "
"sin sos an cluiche agus taispeáin an roghchlár sos."

msgid ""
"Finally, connect the menu's close button to a new method in the script. "
"Inside that method, unpause the game and hide the pause menu."
msgstr ""
"Faoi dheireadh, ceangail cnaipe dlúth an roghchláir le modh nua sa script. "
"Taobh istigh den mhodh sin, déan an cluiche a dhíchur agus folaigh an "
"roghchlár sos."

msgid "You should now have a working pause menu."
msgstr "Ba chóir go mbeadh roghchlár sos oibre agat anois."
